snippet.title: My first mobile game!
snippet.description:
Try to survive each level by keeping the ball in the circle.
Over 15 levels to complete and 9 balls to collect. And even more coming!
For download now: 
https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.opportunitiesgames.Roundy
